{"tid":1388672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實回歸和理非式\"送頭\"才是最大殺傷力","createTime":"2019-07-30T17:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T22:49:41.000Z","uid":287772,"like":11,"dislike":129,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"e84627c660cdbcf822b022d761f537bb538db9f1","tid":1388672,"uid":287772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:55:48.000Z","msg":"<ins>背景</ins><br />\n大家記唔記得2014年12月15日,金鐘佔領區清場, 各路超和理非人馬(hocc/李柱銘之類)坐定定等黑警一個一個來抬走(我稱之為&quot;和理非式送頭&quot;),  黑警無藉口打人尤其有頭有面個d, 抬都抬左12個鐘(我全日在場, 中午抬到半夜).<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>策略</ins><br />\n重點你坐／訓在地上, 唔打人唔鬧人, 佢推你都推唔郁, 衣規拒只能抬走, 和平佔路最多告你無反對通知書集會, 罰款加社會服務(總之好小野), 重點係今天咁多人被告，如果勇武派肯停一次等和理非出手，真可以call到極超多，最小幾千和理非人出面做, 星期日庶打花園一批就是。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>關鍵</ins><br />\n1) 非常容易call到成千上萬人坐定佔路.佢清人都要成日, 又無藉口打人/出tear gas. (如果夠疆出tear gas, 即又大衰輿論一次, 同721效果)<br />\n<br />\n2) 之後佢告幾千人最多罰款/社會服務既小罪, 差人都做唔切, 做一個case minimum工夫唔少，如果幾千個case做到佢死。除事投降唔告。<br />\n<br />\n3)<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">如果唔告就係重點，即係鼓勵大家再出來佔路坐定定唔走，逼佢出武力趕一班和理非人或繼續<span style=\"color: red;\">投降</span>唔告人</span></span></strong></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">逼黑警<span style=\"color: red;\">投降唔俈人</span>先係重點</span></span>"},{"pid":"b474df8ec086e6a85ef8c585232104861da762bc","tid":1388672,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:56:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">後日(8月1)1500-2000</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\nTG:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkrevolutiondocument&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kU2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=50201def\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument</a><br />\nFB:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-100576917956000/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%259B%25B8-100576917956000%2F&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kU2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=c984e4f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-100576917956000/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">餓住的小朋友入一入黎, 有心幫佢地都可以黎睇下</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1382980/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1382980/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地係今日係旺角東天橋擺街站的手足</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1387289/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1387289/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"4322eb0c560bb96aaf78a6618b4ca49e7a945fd1","tid":1388672,"uid":270607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:56:44.000Z","msg":"[img][/img]"},{"pid":"ab40e3df449a4f749e2769d49066e185be211607","tid":1388672,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:56:51.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"5ff530bfa302247fdb581a04f88bc6d132673956","tid":1388672,"uid":220701,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:57:43.000Z","msg":"唔認同<br />\n點解唔hit and run? 引到人大班人嚟 然後即走<br />\n我地0成本可言"},{"pid":"db739ea93f49bfe4c32c0293f49c69c9d73f4545","tid":1388672,"uid":215717,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:59:13.000Z","msg":"進化左做流水抗爭<br />\n你居然想退化<br />\nP牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cae54ccaaf4bbf31b0bff46684a6a82275a2599","tid":1388672,"uid":57566,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:59:44.000Z","msg":"依家點同當年<br />\n依家班狗你坐定定係到都會打柒你發洩"},{"pid":"c4c34137bf13e0b889b62e5fa30e0381eed42e05","tid":1388672,"uid":287772,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"5ff530bfa302247fdb581a04f88bc6d132673956","tid":1388672,"uid":220701,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:57:43.000Z","msg":"唔認同<br />\n點解唔hit and run? 引到人大班人嚟 然後即走<br />\n我地0成本可言"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:00:51.000Z","msg":"hit and run佢都有藉口清場, 事前在傳媒前坐定定, 狗<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">完全沒有任何藉口用武力清場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>斷佢藉口是重點</strong></span>"},{"pid":"d2697881dec7e7c3ac01f753b27c12e3a1bc0958","tid":1388672,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:01:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DErY1NGl2p_M&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kU2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=23155336\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kU2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=7338e3fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong! <br />\nThe Revolution Of Our Times! </span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>五大訴求</strong></span></span></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>Hongkongers 5 Demands:</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n1. Full Withdrawal of the Extradition Bill<br />\n2. Retraction of the Characterisation of the Protestas a Riot<br />\n3. Release all Arrested Protesters<br />\n4. Accountability for Police and Yuen Long White Shirts Brutality<br />\n5. Implement Dual Universal Suffrage"},{"pid":"f4d42804b46b12fffdbb89db8593e1eef02d9c7f","tid":1388672,"uid":287772,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"db739ea93f49bfe4c32c0293f49c69c9d73f4545","tid":1388672,"uid":215717,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:59:13.000Z","msg":"進化左做流水抗爭<br />\n你居然想退化<br />\nP牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:03:20.000Z","msg":"乜野叫<em>退化</em>? 勇武派的思想盲點, 有用就係好方法, 無退唔退化之分"},{"pid":"87da20006514324c9728b2374f5a09df0b7c5750","tid":1388672,"uid":27670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:03:52.000Z","msg":"黑警驚我地真be water 即刻上黎講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9afc4732b25576e973428715213b033ff512c8","tid":1388672,"uid":27670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:04:31.000Z","msg":"香港人唔會再做你地個沙包<br />\n睇路呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55e150cb57f01d2f7e1916ff3a8fcf435725af7","tid":1388672,"uid":8301,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:05:17.000Z","msg":"咁雨革一早成功咗啦弱柒智"},{"pid":"b50328934734e0db5b1e019b4b0f5eb349ca6ece","tid":1388672,"uid":287772,"li